#: ../customize/reactor.rst:3
msgid "Info Reactor"
msgstr "Info 响应器"

#: ../customize/reactor.rst:5
msgid ""
"Info reactors are the components to react to a parsed ``Info`` instance. "
"MCDR uses reactors to trigger command parsing or dispatch plugin events"
msgstr "Info 响应器是响应 ``Info`` 实例的组件。MCDR 使用响应器触发命令解析或插件分发事件。"

#: ../customize/reactor.rst:7
msgid ""
"If you want to add more behaviors to MCDR, like dispatching new events "
"and so on, rather than use a plugin, you can design you own info reactor."
" Since info reactors can access to the inner ``MCDReforgedServer`` "
"instance which is the core object of MCDR, so it may have much more "
"possible usages. But yes, as always, use with cautions"
msgstr ""
"如果你想向 MCDR 添加更多的行为，比如分发新的事件等，你可以设计自己的信息响应器。信息响应器可以访问 "
"``MCDReforgedServer`` 实例——这是 MCDR 的核心对象。因此它有更多可能的用法。不过同样的，和以往一样，请谨慎使用。"

#: ../customize/reactor.rst:9
msgid ""
"Similar to `custom server handler <handler>`__\\ , you info reactor class"
" needs to inherit from the class ``AbstractInfoReactor``. Then you need "
"to implement the ``react`` method to give it some functionalities"
msgstr ""
"与 `自定义处理器 <handler>`__ 相似，你的 Info 响应器类需要从抽象类 ``InfoReactor`` 继承。然后，你需要实现 "
"``react`` 方法以给它添加一些功能。"

#: ../customize/reactor.rst:11
msgid ""
"After you finish coding your reactor, you need to add you reactor class "
"path to the `custom_info_reactors <../configure.html#custom-info-"
"reactors>`__ option of the configure file, then your reactor will start "
"working automatically"
msgstr ""
"完成对响应器编写后， 你需要将响应器类路径添加到配置文件的 `custom_info_reactors <../configure.html"
"#custom-info-reactors>`__ 选项中，然后你的响应器将开始工作。"

